3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper proposes an optimization approach to find a local optimum solution, which is a systems and control problem. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper discusses compress-and-forward schemes, which are commonly used in multimedia applications. 
5. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper proposes an efficient algorithm for allocating backhaul capacities, which is a data structures and algorithms problem.
